step_data.thought: The current page shows an error message stating that we can't add the item to the Wish List right now: Cannot add product without stock to wishlist.. This indicates that the product is out of stock. Since the page doesn't provide an option to add the product to the wish list, we should inform the user that the product is unavailable for wishlisting due to stock issues.
